            <description><![CDATA[<p>Release date: 2026-05-13</p>
<h2 id="new">New</h2>
<h2 id="improvements">Improvements</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Made saved templates more reliable.</strong> Your templates
and custom prompts are now more likely to stay available after app
updates, relaunches, or Finder Quick Action use.</li>
<li><strong>Improved template syncing with Finder Quick
Actions.</strong> Templates used from Finder now stay better aligned
with the ones you saved in the app.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="bug-fixes">Bug Fixes</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Fixed the Automation permission row getting stuck.</strong>
First-run users now see the Grant Access option when Automation
permission has not been decided yet, and the row updates right after
they respond.</li>
<li><strong>Fixed a bug where templates and custom prompts could
disappear.</strong> Saved naming templates and custom prompts should now
remain available instead of unexpectedly resetting.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
